    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Dutch-style gardens, distinctive geometric and symmetrical designs, especially prominent in the seventeenth and eighteenth centuries; found also in countries other than the Netherlands.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
